1
00:00:00,834 --> 00:00:01,902
DAVIS:
<i>ExVeemon and I decided</i>

2
00:00:01,935 --> 00:00:03,504
<i>to take on MaloMyotismon,</i>

3
00:00:03,537 --> 00:00:05,239
<i>even though the others</i>
<i>were afraid of him.</i>

4
00:00:05,272 --> 00:00:06,740
<i>I don't blame them.</i>

5
00:00:06,773 --> 00:00:08,442
<i>If ever stopped</i>
<i>to think about anything,</i>

6
00:00:08,475 --> 00:00:10,110
<i>I'd be scared too!</i>

7
00:00:10,143 --> 00:00:12,579
<i>MaloMyotismon played</i>
<i>mind tricks on everyone,</i>

8
00:00:12,613 --> 00:00:14,114
<i>terrifying Ken</i>
<i>and making the others</i>

9
00:00:14,147 --> 00:00:16,016
<i>believe their favorite</i>
<i>wish had come true!</i>

10
00:00:16,049 --> 00:00:17,851
<i>But my wish really</i>
<i>did come true</i>

11
00:00:17,885 --> 00:00:20,287
<i>because Veemon digivolved</i>
<i>into all his forms</i>

12
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:21,355
<i>at the same time!</i>

13
00:00:21,388 --> 00:00:23,023
<i>That's the good news.</i>

14
00:00:23,056 --> 00:00:25,192
<i>The bad news is that</i>
<i>MaloMyotismon's wishes</i>

15
00:00:25,225 --> 00:00:26,860
<i>are also coming true,</i>

16
00:00:26,894 --> 00:00:28,896
<i>and his wishes could make</i>
<i>a genie crawl back</i>

17
00:00:28,929 --> 00:00:30,364
<i>in his bottle!</i>

18
00:00:30,397 --> 00:00:32,332
(electronic music)

19
